Marrakech,05QDGvi0_sM,UgzCpNHUAEk5pISu0cJ4AaABAg.AW7aiEauLO-AW8X6hJlQAv,UgzCpNHUAEk5pISu0cJ4AaABAg,@FindingGinaMarie,"Hi @nsaxen4 Uber didn't operate there when we were there, but Uber relaunched in Marrakech and Casablanca in November 2025. There aren't plans for it to have a presence in any other Moroccan cities, though. We needed to use a petite cab when we needed to get around outside the Medina in Fes. Here's our full series. If you are visiting Morocco, we hope you consider Fes. We also did a Sahara Desert tour! —Judy
