Marrakech,05QDGvi0_sM,Ugw7a45JQ1LH6NfVopV4AaABAg.AAWZ6K3mxNBAAa__lERbgk,Ugw7a45JQ1LH6NfVopV4AaABAg,@FindingGinaMarie,I think it is supposed to be more interesting than Casablanca. Although our walking tour guide really didn't recommend anyplace other than Marrakech and Fes except for taking day trips. He specifically discouraged people from visiting Casablanca because of how industrial it is (which seemed to be the general consensus). —Judy,2024-11-08T21:52:37Z,2024-11-08T21:52:37Z,0,True,,2026-05-13T02:01:49.969795
Marrakech,05QDGvi0_sM,Ugw7a45JQ1LH6NfVopV4AaABAg.AAWZ6K3mxNBAAg6gLrMqW1,Ugw7a45JQ1LH6NfVopV4AaABAg,@dotted8-,"@FindingGinaMarie But you could go visit the replica, Rick’s American Cafe in Casablanca.",2024-11-11T01:26:49Z,2024-11-11T01:26:49Z,0,True,,2026-05-13T02:01:49.969800
